TCP Port Scanner import java.net.*; public class TCPPortScanner { public static void main(String args[]) { for (int port=1l; port<=65535; port++) { try { Socket socket = new Socket("127.0.0.1",port); System.out.println("Port in use: " + port ); socket.close() ; } catch (Exception e) { System.out.println("Port not in use: " + port ); } }o} }
